commitResults.messageTitle: Add Undo, Redo, and History commands
commitResults.messageBody:
There is no undo, redo and history commands available.

The application should have these functionalities for a better user
experience.

Let's
- Add a new VersionedAddressBook class
- Add Undo, Redo and History commands
- Update the parser to recognize these commands
- Add and update test cases to ensure the new features work correctly

A new class VersionedAddressBook extends AddressBook to support the
new functionalities by saving each version of the AddressBook whenever
it is modified.
